      "title": "Rs. 30Mn worth gold seized at BIA",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); A stock of gold worth more than Rs. 30 million was seized by the customs personnel at the Bandaranaike International Airport on Friday (26).",
        "Sri Lanka Customs said that the relevant gold stock weighing over 2 kg was in the possession of a passenger who had come to Sri Lanka from Paris.",
        "The estimated value of the stock of gold is Rs. 36,219,000/-."
